Description:
wrappers that don't throw invalid parameter notifications with MSVC runtime
libraries

Files:
lib/msvc-nothrow.h
lib/msvc-nothrow.c
m4/msvc-nothrow.m4

Depends-on:
msvc-inval

configure.ac:
AC_REQUIRE([gl_MSVC_NOTHROW])
if test $HAVE_MSVC_INVALID_PARAMETER_HANDLER = 1; then
  AC_LIBOBJ([msvc-nothrow])
fi

Makefile.am:

Include:
"msvc-nothrow.h"

